bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://shoptalkshow.com/697/\" target=\"_blank\">https://shoptalkshow.com/697/</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"148\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100062010\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=afabd7fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5efZzm59B9j1VwNWSByF6hcGdBOQbOcVIy3X0IkVFFA9icoeI8WDjbJ9az6rwic7WhlIU86MB9bcDYw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">Syntax：970 - Anthropic 为什么收购 Bun？</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 问答环节：Git GUI vs 终端、实验性项目与可访问性的平衡、如何阻止恶意流量、智能家居设置、Anthropic 收购 Bun 的原因、处理难搞的队友。Wes 和 Scott 的回答很直接，从工具选择到团队管理都有涉及。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0p